рџЏіпёЏвЂЌвљ§пёЏ prints every ascii value from 0-255 with its corresponding ANSI colour

a;wa >:3                       рџЏіпёЏвЂЌвљ§пёЏ push 0, sub 1 to overflow to 255 for equality check later
alskdjfhl >//////< :333 wa >:3 рџЏіпёЏвЂЌвљ§пёЏ start counter at 31 (ASCII values before 32 are mainly control codes, so we don't include them)

